Here's the latest news regarding Donald Trump as of July 4, 2025:

**"One Big Beautiful Bill" (OBBB):**

President Trump's signature legislation, referred to as the "One Big Beautiful Bill," has passed both the US House of Representatives [cbsnews](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQERZgjKfYvIBANIOpq1VK72hlDShTwqr0cierUp3WG0_JA8E7jJyNbpaYP2RUIXxtD3tu9CDPT2aWwX9gi6vgH4f76WoPFuVYzleTunRKYSIxDlPrpTlebbkN0D1j9Qoq9jaH3zEV7BbhDed7ZJjtUyzoEMBx_R-mtypVIkb0KBFdgjSHdTzEvI9CDQWyLYkmFZVG8BEISfnBfaL4UlT1rhXK4=) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdJKeiIyR0VdDL-C-HPrnBFPwm4NsA7_gNAvSJqD---CnixVnv-ckCaFg3gC4XGuEpyCQJQ2kUAkDaYATr-dZB1XiH2PE-xbEdLLkI58uHwSS-89ihY3N8O84SQzIhTWtpEIKwO1wwLugy8belZr0lDXDEDk7kBCA9NR8D5xy46MzKIJbyHRVJ66EHrzPZ4DMGv7KyZFdusesBq1lFsmMXCMitYw4C2LjmUxsHbZiMJO4jew==) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6ebzfwi1Ltsr6Bjjk6_kbRcfv8dCPzTZGxnoI3-bYx8UC6PdyElQLvvn5YV8efeIrsQtd_cOAF_UdxVd0dWVZxYmjvWIkbmCd2Sgxa5FNSm7Ms3YalhuiJc9fBFcjk1plXu7tfB0uYtHln6pvs4iXx3jnce2NQ-BdEWdsmyShIctLOK8vjpx44fUjvtW1pZi5d9r6z2OP3mPUZyg_LH0Y) [newsweek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=) [hklaw](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGacpQTmmVWNKbYK6czhK85rN8kYXOGMXDlXN2YxhGi4dCi8PXJonasj8tQJv-tam1nFh70ddqtxFT0wYmr03SXQLkD9x_QPcVlGs7kheFC5OOpvmVNxENgi-yprEZVCXl4feCE9DUPkBCH_vXiIOx75M-1QlN7dl08eM19COEbDMdGs_6E1UqTG6xFSUW0fdsYkhsdUPHRkUp7m8HCkvyjvZ-dERV9vrZ7). The House vote was 218 to 214, largely along party lines [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdJKeiIyR0VdDL-C-HPrnBFPwm4NsA7_gNAvSJqD---CnixVnv-ckCaFg3gC4XGuEpyCQJQ2kUAkDaYATr-dZB1XiH2PE-xbEdLLkI58uHwSS-89ihY3N8O84SQzIhTWtpEIKwO1wwLugy8belZr0lDXDEDk7kBCA9NR8D5xy46MzKIJbyHRVJ66EHrzPZ4DMGv7KyZFdusesBq1lFsmMXCMitYw4C2LjmUxsHbZiMJO4jew==). The Senate vote was 51-50, with Vice President JD Vance breaking a tie [politicopro](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE6YmBQVQPspDwMS_5O5qe6k2v5l2H0is2Idm5F0-51Mzc9QilTAcveL3ztwsBOfodXyd81FTXNDa7PphOX9G7OSrHCa-rJrNyvvj0rpUUFtCp0Y7PkegGsPvpqczpFC8Cn2jRuoNF56izm_tUSQ4S2kB3kUWG2GnboqQbUJExT8ELTS-_AG9BO8ETfNFGOAyOByZNxohMe). Trump is expected to sign the bill into law in a White House ceremony today, July 4th [cbsnews](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQERZgjKfYvIBANIOpq1VK72hlDShTwqr0cierUp3WG0_JA8E7jJyNbpaYP2RUIXxtD3tu9CDPT2aWwX9gi6vgH4f76WoPFuVYzleTunRKYSIxDlPrpTlebbkN0D1j9Qoq9jaH3zEV7BbhDed7ZJjtUyzoEMBx_R-mtypVIkb0KBFdgjSHdTzEvI9CDQWyLYkmFZVG8BEISfnBfaL4UlT1rhXK4=) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdJKeiIyR0VdDL-C-HPrnBFPwm4NsA7_gNAvSJqD---CnixVnv-ckCaFg3gC4XGuEpyCQJQ2kUAkDaYATr-dZB1XiH2PE-xbEdLLkI58uHwSS-89ihY3N8O84SQzIhTWtpEIKwO1wwLugy8belZr0lDXDEDk7kBCA9NR8D5xy46MzKIJbyHRVJ66EHrzPZ4DMGv7KyZFdusesBq1lFsmMXCMitYw4C2LjmUxsHbZiMJO4jew==) [politico](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_9fQfxuFuoAA33b9lHgLqQxGFhVXwpvdgoXz08K7rUccFuc_Zqh6fq6AKHufzI__QmXt7i5DzFdHk1njwnYgb0Uo02oPh3A9otmTLtotZB14sDCUXDRKf5wc1WpoFvjDBfk86U-1CNGWnr9kDUL88aRA4RROd4FhlbzCicIzF2bvDhJI=).

The OBBB is a sweeping piece of legislation that combines extensions to the 2017 tax cuts, increased spending on defense and border security, overhauls social safety-net programs, increases border and military spending, and raises the federal debt ceiling by $5 trillion [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-Pff0cd_JUfw5vx2cqdKDVJh5A5YWhgjRUk_ABytaoZzPix_zjkVZF8W8PsY-6kI0BPHv_73Xmvt17TmJfp7Aykhd18dYEfuJyoq2jtv3CNzGA0Ze-rlKy4si51ih9TnXD0ozeJpBzu7PaV-uYG7bFlk8fNwcHpn24BegCJQWlNOqDmFJmxrFE8nZ3E1KfuMUJInb7yHyl_dYv5RGOMXolQS3ow==) [politicopro](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE6YmBQVQPspDwMS_5O5qe6k2v5l2H0is2Idm5F0-51Mzc9QilTAcveL3ztwsBOfodXyd81FTXNDa7PphOX9G7OSrHCa-rJrNyvvj0rpUUFtCp0Y7PkegGsPvpqczpFC8Cn2jRuoNF56izm_tUSQ4S2kB3kUWG2GnboqQbUJExT8ELTS-_AG9BO8ETfNFGOAyOByZNxohMe).

**Key Aspects and Impacts of the OBBB:**

*   **Social Safety-Net Amendments:** The bill includes significant changes to Medicaid and SNAP [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-Pff0cd_JUfw5vx2cqdKDVJh5A5YWhgjRUk_ABytaoZzPix_zjkVZF8W8PsY-6kI0BPHv_73Xmvt17TmJfp7Aykhd18dYEfuJyoq2jtv3CNzGA0Ze-rlKy4si51ih9TnXD0ozeJpBzu7PaV-uYG7bFlk8fNwcHpn24BegCJQWlNOqDmFJmxrFE8nZ3E1KfuMUJInb7yHyl_dYv5RGOMXolQS3ow==). It cuts nearly $1 trillion from Medicaid [aha](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFk6WH_EihqQNY3DTM5LauY23e_8HL2tOypI-EmNRvDFmPLIvQs6EXmNWbrWiVnwGCijI8hdrGRQ-rpsaZOvnQ8c72wU_3Ymnc9coeswj8F_ccKGSDz5kphQznK1ZeoJLN0YtPXiXYERgBJuzta_H_a_tH5qAYI_1IBFuXWbuqPhgh-vKkGD1825kbQ_mTq3A2jQ0102wswHHYEBAo) [nysfocus](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFM-cn3Ob_IRmkXGVJgZdZjSjvcfseRb8GemqORW8aKmUAIKmdZ41Y0xuDWilOwcs0mdZ7O8Iv9CKa64tDKuMUGosyIcKBZqusKjF-ylwz-Lsx1lSCCrvscL_pwAvYBgqun5Hfw_-7WMIWtAhYzmDW3QMN5zsGgZIfk8QdE), potentially leading to millions losing healthcare coverage [georgetown](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH8E0tg8PuwTm6CMEBZqnEKo_QZPdN6njyfZZ0XKYHvGcMU4kumZlE2ln-7sxpzXMemGee4n9OqP-uie-ZuRl_2hYMd-YKyiICU65n-mwcaxYci8D_e6uLaUMnXQgnJUl169FXZcKj1459hTaCCcMm7hD_qKIyxpUWYMKeEs_gKQ5cvpzq1jg0KMPtXxM_I3RRbIdX2Nocxtzc_97UtBpxxZDuaM1ilAA==) [georgetown](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHv00v2cAeCLQmFxnTL8oyAE56YmRypWJK0VaIT9Zla6D4250IA0l2G2XkEP3xqq7NIPi4rQucIkFzfZpA0YPowcIYrt5EMgQtIWFvgIa_hF6ePVmgSwL3Kbe5Ht6dAnBp_54tEo_n3u1XGL5BAxmCTjB0fSbKoEGbT1JsYsHkgdNi3NMDRlTDm71aIcpKiJkGhs38bph8QyqJHYPVUJPHlBgWNEIbNuHxfnA==). There are also over $200 billion in cuts to SNAP [nysfocus](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFM-cn3Ob_IRmkXGVJgZdZjSjvcfseRb8GemqORW8aKmUAIKmdZ41Y0xuDWilOwcs0mdZ7O8Iv9CKa64tDKuMUGosyIcKBZqusKjF-ylwz-Lsx1lSCCrvscL_pwAvYBgqun5Hfw_-7WMIWtAhYzmDW3QMN5zsGgZIfk8QdE), with tighter work requirements and other restrictions [hklaw](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEOq5C5NFxwZRIAKJ6Xutmm-4nlMGzydp8QWrPsi7kyKfNZGiil0CnLnGDXvIasQyuYyODUs02HZS3VmrS4cM8w9zlTVRiry7jbTFgFyGBdzL56iSOmrJWIBCfTEhnR9tBt7N4DWmDOrxUhqPE50N-P94oQtFe6s6hUgqaIPKK692POERzII3TSE_zvJvY-bktZBvuPcdbL0FNcHbJKFAtXb70Ugd_9kw==). A $6,000 tax deduction for individuals aged 65 or older with income up to $75,000, or up to $150,000 for married couples is enacted [newsweek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=).

*   **Projected Impacts:** The CBO estimates the bill will increase the number of uninsured people by 17 million over the next 10 years [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6ebzfwi1Ltsr6Bjjk6_kbRcfv8dCPzTZGxnoI3-bYx8UC6PdyElQLvvn5YV8efeIrsQtd_cOAF_UdxVd0dWVZxYmjvWIkbmCd2Sgxa5FNSm7Ms3YalhuiJc9fBFcjk1plXu7tfB0uYtHln6pvs4iXx3jnce2NQ-BdEWdsmyShIctLOK8vjpx44fUjvtW1pZi5d9r6z2OP3mPUZyg_LH0Y). Millions could lose Medicaid coverage and SNAP benefits could be reduced or eliminated for over one million New Yorkers, including children [nysfocus](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFM-cn3Ob_IRmkXGVJgZdZjSjvcfseRb8GemqORW8aKmUAIKmdZ41Y0xuDWilOwcs0mdZ7O8Iv9CKa64tDKuMUGosyIcKBZqusKjF-ylwz-Lsx1lSCCrvscL_pwAvYBgqun5Hfw_-7WMIWtAhYzmDW3QMN5zsGgZIfk8QdE). The bill is projected to disproportionately affect low-income adults without dependents [georgetown](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHv00v2cAeCLQmFxnTL8oyAE56YmRypWJK0VaIT9Zla6D4250IA0l2G2XkEP3xqq7NIPi4rQucIkFzfZpA0YPowcIYrt5EMgQtIWFvgIa_hF6ePVmgSwL3Kbe5Ht6dAnBp_54tEo_n3u1XGL5BAxmCTjB0fSbKoEGbT1JsYsHkgdNi3NMDRlTDm71aIcpKiJkGhs38bph8QyqJHYPVUJPHlBgWNEIbNuHxfnA==) and may disproportionately affect rural communities [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6ebzfwi1Ltsr6Bjjk6_kbRcfv8dCPzTZGxnoI3-bYx8UC6PdyElQLvvn5YV8efeIrsQtd_cOAF_UdxVd0dWVZxYmjvWIkbmCd2Sgxa5FNSm7Ms3YalhuiJc9fBFcjk1plXu7tfB0uYtHln6pvs4iXx3jnce2NQ-BdEWdsmyShIctLOK8vjpx44fUjvtW1pZi5d9r6z2OP3mPUZyg_LH0Y) [whitehouse](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=0]. Almost 90 percent of Social Security recipients will no longer be required to pay income taxes on their benefits due to a new tax deduction [newsweek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=). The CBO estimates that the bill will increase the U.S. debt by $3.3 trillion over the next 10 years [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6ebzfwi1Ltsr6Bjjk6_kbRcfv8dCPzTZGxnoI3-bYx8UC6PdyElQLvvn5YV8efeIrsQtd_cOAF_UdxVd0dWVZxYmjvWIkbmCd2Sgxa5FNSm7Ms3YalhuiJc9fBFcjk1plXu7tfB0uYtHln6pvs4iXx3jnce2NQ-BdEWdsmyShIctLOK8vjpx44fUjvtW1pZi5d9r6z2OP3mPUZyg_LH0Y) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-Pff0cd_JUfw5vx2cqdKDVJh5A5YWhgjRUk_ABytaoZzPix_zjkVZF8W8PsY-6kI0BPHv_73Xmvt17TmJfp7Aykhd18dYEfuJyoq2jtv3CNzGA0Ze-rlKy4si51ih9TnXD0ozeJpBzu7PaV-uYG7bFlk8fNwcHpn24BegCJQWlNOqDmFJmxrFE8nZ3E1KfuMUJInb7yHyl_dYv5RGOMXolQS3ow==).

*   **Arguments For and Against:** Proponents argue the bill will fuel economic growth, cut waste and fraud, and strengthen programs like Medicaid with reforms [whitehouse](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=0) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6ebzfwi1Ltsr6Bjjk6_kbRcfv8dCPzTZGxnoI3-bYx8UC6PdyElQLvvn5YV8efeIrsQtd_cOAF_UdxVd0dWVZxYmjvWIkbmCd2Sgxa5FNSm7Ms3YalhuiJc9fBFcjk1plXu7tfB0uYtHln6pvs4iXx3jnce2NQ-BdEWdsmyShIctLOK8vjpx44fUjvtW1pZi5d9r6z2OP3mPUZyg_LH0Y) [house](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=2) [newsweek](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=). Opponents argue it will increase the deficit, cut essential safety net programs, and disproportionately benefit the wealthy [texastribune](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGtYKbcXfcySobkP8MbgKOpgY0Wun9b0v3Yijq67bRsrOGJRbRIKCTT47ltPIEGHgVhywHaVoPk9LlZtEpUO_YxIb0cPJ2wuY-bFLW5Ot6bRsI_KCTL8ZeCOQ8Q-kz4YBvzZLnIvayUD0lOlJ33olWeG9R8KTD6EFvzjATvDkjpwkz8c8zFrZkCLk4-C66rLHFnRWj34LPh) [time](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjCVt-rPdx62AuJCYDwYUF07NluI2WEbszmWa3aAcdlTCJjHlUqtXr1uMu0Jke8XXQS2cgqSilz389TWf9gk4odkdzW_fbdd3QarHGTO4HhySqa6kn_mVdSttsh2S6mDvWGF7PThs2Fm5nTiyR6IZUhIdrqyRcavCxxHSu9rDQfIQS9pJqc5Gc6ZUJJB0=3) [aha](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFk6WH_EihqQNY3DTM5LauY23e_8HL2tOypI-EmNRvDFmPLIvQs6EXmNWbrWiVnwGCijI8hdrGRQ-rpsaZOvnQ8c72wU_3Ymnc9coeswj8F_ccKGSDz5kphQznK1ZeoJLN0YtPXiXYERgBJuzta_H_a_tH5qAYI_1IBFuXWbuqPhgh-vKkGD1825kbQ_mTq3A2jQ0102wswHHYEBAo).

**Other Recent News:**

*   **International Relations:** Trump stated there was no progress on Ukraine in a call with Putin [politico](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_XH3w7JOaR6rOyN1sC5TdojsTTaYWflHkxPyhUPXaISZR-9jOmOYDNRseA9cpqs8jksEtfCEfvr2BUrb4UuNc9cpsJPt-7fUCT52dInNJ_DrNeZEjyOGK2xmPLN7sE-6iDAVUqA==). He also announced a deal to impose a 20% tariff on trade with Vietnam [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdJKeiIyR0VdDL-C-HPrnBFPwm4NsA7_gNAvSJqD---CnixVnv-ckCaFg3gC4XGuEpyCQJQ2kUAkDaYATr-dZB1XiH2PE-xbEdLLkI58uHwSS-89ihY3N8O84SQzIhTWtpEIKwO1wwLugy8belZr0lDXDEDk7kBCA9NR8D5xy46MzKIJbyHRVJ66EHrzPZ4DMGv7KyZFdusesBq1lFsmMXCMitYw4C2LjmUxsHbZiMJO4jew==). Trump says Israel has agreed to finalize a 60-day Gaza ceasefire and urges Hamas to accept the deal [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEpZu1QtYCzsBJXfbUBPP3diNEFdTA25G0LKClBPAtdUWhpfXGTBRjlT4T0nSxpZkjhbf2KXDK3EeLgciH379PsLIJy5L7dGCeulaQiY3uUidGCbhzHQgxfNJdQVBRnFJls-amJTXo=).
*   **Immigration:** A judge blocked a "sweeping" asylum crackdown after Trump declared an "invasion" at the southern border [politico](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_XH3w7JOaR6rOyN1sC5TdojsTTaYWflHkxPyhUPXaISZR-9jOmOYDNRseA9cpqs8jksEtfCEfvr2BUrb4UuNc9cpsJPt-7fUCT52dInNJ_DrNeZEjyOGK2xmPLN7sE-6iDAVUqA==) [aljazeera](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEpZu1QtYCzsBJXfbUBPP3diNEFdTA25G0LKClBPAtdUWhpfXGTBRjlT4T0nSxpZkjhbf2KXDK3EeLgciH379PsLIJy5L7dGCeulaQiY3uUidGCbhzHQgxfNJdQVBRnFJls-amJTXo=).
